metadata.name: ILL (WYTWM)
metadata.description:
This song was written over Christmas.  

Itâ€™s been a strange start the year. 2023 surely is going to be an interesting one. From me and the family all being ill, to the ups and downs of life being sometimes overbearing. This is an ode to continuing on regardless. 

This is the first step into a new journey. This collection is called commissions. Made for people who wish to support me and the vision of progressive blockchain expansion by means of creating art. From your friendly neighbourhood singing and songwriting mogul. 

Published with Heartistry copyright original creator Joe Nix for all time.

Thank you for making this possible and use this however you like if you are the holder of it :)

Stay blessed.
